ActDepartment of Citizenship and Immigration Act
Immigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectNew Canada-Northwest Territories Agreement on Territorial Nominees
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Citizenship and Immigration to enter into a renewed five-year AGREEMENT on TERRITORIAL NOMINEES with the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES which will replace the existing CANADA-NORTHWEST TERRITORIES AGREEMENT ON PROVINCIAL NOMINEES which will expire on August 10, 2013.
